{
  "llm": {
    "freeform_prompt": [
      "识别英语练习单（可能多页），输出JSON：",
      "{\"sections\":[{\"title\":\"一、单词默写(15个)\",\"type\":\"WORD\",\"items\":[",
      "{\"q\":1,\"hint\":\"尾巴\",\"ans\":\"tail\",\"ok\":true,\"conf\":1.0,\"pg\":0,\"note\":\"\"},",
      "{\"q\":2,\"hint\":\"农场\",\"ans\":\"farm\",\"ok\":true,\"conf\":1.0,\"pg\":1,\"note\":\"\"}",
      "]}]}",
      "",
      "字段：title=大题标题，type=WORD/PHRASE/SENTENCE，q=题号(section内从1起)，hint=中文提示(不含序号)，ans=学生答案，ok=正确性，conf=置信度0-1，pg=页码(第1张=0,第2张=1)，note=备注",
      "",
      "要求：",
      "1.按题号顺序，识别大题标题和类型",
      "2.未作答：ans空，ok=false，note=\"未作答\"",
      "3.判断正确性：考虑拼写/语法/大小写",
      "4.**重点**：观察每题在哪张图，准确标记pg。不同题可能在不同页",
      "5.返回纯JSON"
    ]
  },
  "ocr": {
    "provider": "baidu",
    "endpoint": "https://aip.baidubce.com/rest/2.0/ocr/v1/doc_analysis",
    "scene": "doc_analysis",
    "params": {
      "language_type": "CHN_ENG",
      "result_type": "big",
      "detect_direction": "true",
      "words_type": "handprint_mix",
      "line_probability": "true"
    },
    "notes": "试卷分析与识别（doc_analysis）"
  }
}
